<p><span style="font-size:larger;">Showcase for the best audio adaptations of articles on this wiki and on <a href="#wl">The Wanderers' Library</a>.</span></p>
<p>The • symbol marks adaptations that are not completely faithful to the source material (for example sibstituting in words where there are redactions), or missing supplemental pages or sections of the main article (for example skipping the Containment Procedures).<br />
<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<div class="collapsible-block">
