<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<div style="text-align: left;">
<ul>
<li>Edit the following pages:
<ul>
<li><a href="/scp-series-6-audio-edition">SCP Series 6 - Audio Edition</a></li>
<li><a href="/scp-series-5-audio-edition">SCP Series 5 - Audio Edition</a></li>
