</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>For every other type of article edit the lists at the bottom of this page.</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>If you see that a line you are adding to is commented out <tt><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[!--like&#32;this--]</span></tt>, remove the <tt><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[!--</span></tt> and <tt><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">--]</span></tt> to un-comment and un-hide that line.</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>The name in the &quot;Audio Links&quot; column must be under 20 characters long.</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>Mark with the • symbol adaptations that are not completely faithful to the source material (for example sibstituting in words where there are redactions), or missing supplemental pages or sections of the main article (for example skipping the Containment Procedures).<br />
<strong>Example:</strong> <a href="https://youtu.be/imH-Tx9aQI0">SCPReadings•</a></li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>Please leave a descriptive <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/audio-adaptations/revision-note.png">revision note</a>.</li>
</ul>
<p>To control bloat there is a limit of three adaptations per article. Feel free to add new readings in excess of the limit, but this page's maintainers will occasionally prune the lists down to three again, keeping the adaptations that offer the best experience.</p>
